{ If you took the Rook with  1...Nxh1  , then you missed the chance to set up the prettiest mate ever! 5 push-ups as punishment! }
2. Kd2 Be3#
{ Even without Queens, minor pieces can swarm an open King.  From Dodge - Houghteling, Chicago 1905 }
