{ White has just sacrificed his Queen, how do we follow-up? } 1. Ne7+
{ Double-check!  The King is forced to move!   17.Nf6+??  is the same idea but there is no follow-up and we're just down a Queen. Oops. }
1... Kh8 2. Nxg6# { The fantastic finish to Albin - Shipley, New York 1894. } *

[Event "?"]
