[White "Section II - Common Tactics"]
[Black "Tactical Section - The King's Diagonal 2"]
[Result "*"]

1. e4 e5 2. f4 Bc5 3. fxe5
{ White gets greedy and wins a pawn, but his King's Diagonal is wide open. }
3... Qh4+ 4. Ke2 Qxe4#
{ Whenever your opponent moves his f-pawn without yet castling, the potential for this check is always there. }
