{ Anything on the fifth rank is vulnerable to the Qa5+. } 3... Qa5+
{ Note that if the pawn were not on  e3  , Black could retreat the Bishop to  d2  . }
4. Nc3 Qxg5
{ For this tactic to work, all that is required is   i  an uncastled King,   ii  an open diagonal to check, and  iii  a weakness on the fifth rank to pick up. }
