{ Black has a massive lead in development.  How do we finish White off? } 1...
Qxh3+ { Opens the long diagonal. } 2. gxh3 Bc6+
{ The King is nearly corralled. } 3. Kh2 Bg3#
{ It's useful to study many types of mating combinations, because then you'll be more likely to see similar ideas in your own games.    Taken from NN - Tarrasch, Munich 1932. }
