{ This is a tough one.  Good luck! } 1. Bxf7+
{ First move is thematic, but what is the follow-up? } 1... Kxf7 2. Rxd7+
{ Distracting the Queen!  Once the Queen moves, Ng5 is too strong. } 2... Qxd7
3. Ng5+ Kg8 4. Qxh7# { A beautiful combination from Macdonnel-NN, London 1830 }
