{ How does White increase his lead in development? } 1. Bf3
{ Saving the Rook is a good start. } 1... Qg6 2. Qd2
{ Castling Kingside doesn't work, so White prepares to castle Queenside. } 2...
e5 3. O-O-O
{ And we ignore the threat!  Maximum activity!  White is ready to unleash all matter of unpleasantness in Nimzovich-Alapin, Riga 1913 }
