{ How to continue the attack? } 1. Nxe5
{ Opening the e-file and bringing the Knight into the attack.  1.dxe5?  actually blocks the e-file and loses the Bishop. Oops. }
1... Nxc4
{ In the game Horvath-Mayer, Budapest 1917, Black played f6 here.  What is the refutation if he takes the Bishop? }
2. Bxe7 { Drawing the Queen to the e-file. } 2... Qxe7 3. Nxc4
{ White wins the Queen. } *

