1. Nxg7+ { The Bishop is pinned, so Black's reply is forced. } 1... Ke7 2.
Nhf5+ { Distracting the Rook from the defence of  e6  . } 2... Rxf5 3. Qe6#
{ If I'm honest, this mate in 3 has always been hard for me to see.  Hopefully drilling it will help you because it had helped me.  From Capablanca - Friedman, Karlsbad 1933. }
