{ Many pieces are attacked in Netzer - Mundet Riera, 2006.  How should White react? }
1. Qd8+
{ Remember Morphy's Opera Game?  This is the same motif in a slightly different position.  When you start learning and really absorbing the common patterns, these ideas start jumping out at you instantly. }
1... Qxd8 2. Rxd8# *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
